lemma sum_list_nth_eqI: fixes xs ys::"'a::monoid_add list" shows "length xs = length ys \<Longrightarrow> (\<And>x y. (x, y) \<in> set (zip xs ys) \<Longrightarrow> x = y) \<Longrightarrow> sum_list xs = sum_list ys"
by (induct rule: list_induct2) (auto intro: add_left_imp_eq)
